Pre-Game Insights: Estonia are aiming to get off to a strong start in this season's UEFA Nations League, when they face Slovakia at the A. Le Coq Stadium in Tallinn on Thursday evening (September 5).
Estonia's first away game in this season's Nations League, against Sweden, will be shown live on ETV+ here, with coverage beginning at 9.30 p.m. Estonian time on Saturday, September 8.
